_sText:
This is a multigames map with Crash Bandicoot textures and sounds (only crash 1, 2 and 3) and there are 12 minigames (only 11 aviable at the beginning) like courses, awp or knife battles, bhop and more.

All textures belong from some levels of crash bandicoot 1, 2 and 3, so I thank **FireWavezZ** to learn me how can I use them.

In this map there is an Easter Egg (only aviable in multiplayer servers) that unlock the last minigame.

_If you find bugs, missing textures or glitches, contact me._


Levels style: Lights Out, Spaced Out, Future Frenzy, Tomb Wader, Fumbling In The Dark, Plant Food, Gone Tomorrow, The Lost City, Air Crash, Rock It, Tomb Time, Snow Go.

Minigames:
- Slippery Course
- Dark Castle Course
- Tech Course
- Futuristic AWP
- Knife Waders
- Search & Kill
- River BHOP
- Tomorrow War (not aviable at the begin)
- Jump & Jump
- Ship Battle
- Low Gravity War
- Tomb Deagle
